  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: cf555bfe9da9488cbab3dac7e1bcc86c, type: 3}
  m_Name: Alfonso - Dialogues
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Data.DialogueData
  onGameStart: Wanna play? I go first. Highest card wins, easy right? Your turn.
  thinking:
  - 'Can''t go wrong... or can I? '
  - What to do? ...
  - 'so many choices... '
  - this one... or ... this one?
  - hmm... probably...
  winRound:
  - Ha! That's how it's done.
  - One more for me!
  - Seems I still got it
  loseRound:
  - Hah... okay, you got me there.
  - Ugh.
  - Won't be so easy next round
  - Need some more beer...
  - hah... good play
  onLoseGame: "Well... fair\u2019s fair, I suppose"
  stickerPhase: "Now pick a sticker. Drag it on your card or one on your hand.\nI\u2019ll
    take from what you leave."
  encounterPhase: The winner takes the cards in play. Run out of cards, and you lose.
